                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.6363/478: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Matthews</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-09-28T11:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 28, 1928—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 1:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>110. The Senate committee unanimously approved article 2 of petroleum bill with
                    following addition: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Therefore the competent authority may decree on petition of a
                            legitimately interested party the expropriations necessary for the
                            exercise and development of said industry.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Matthews</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
